{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":78160,"duration_api_ms":77819,"num_turns":3,"result":"**Summary of tools found:**\n\n| Tool | Config | CI? | Pre-commit? |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `bash -n` | `Makefile`, `.github/workflows/test.yml` | Yes | No |\n| `jq empty` | `.github/workflows/test.yml` | Yes | No |\n| `bats-core` | `Dockerfile.test`, `Makefile` | Yes | No |\n| `validate-skill.sh` | `scripts/validate-skill.sh` | No | No |\n| `validate-subagent.sh` | `scripts/validate-subagent.sh` | No | No |\n\n**Key takeaways:**\n\n- This is a pure Bash project — no ESLint, Prettier, ruff, mypy, or similar ecosystem tools.\n- The only automated quality gate in CI is shell syntax checking (`bash -n` on all `.sh` files) and JSON schema validation (`jq empty` on all `schemas/*.json`).\n- The test suite (`bats-core` in Docker) is CI-enforced and uses a mock `claude` binary — no real API calls in tests.\n- The two custom validators (`validate-skill.sh`, `validate-subagent.sh`) run internally during Phase 5 of ultrainit itself but are **not** wired into CI or pre-commit hooks.\n- There are no pre-commit hooks configured anywhere in the project.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"93454300-9e78-4e9f-b543-1b120fa6ef59","total_cost_usd":0.2419784499999999,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":29830,"cache_read_input_tokens":55935,"output_tokens":1714,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":29830,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":332,"cache_read_input_tokens":28974,"cache_creation_input_tokens":856,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":856},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":7,"outputTokens":1714,"cacheReadInputTokens":55935,"cacheCreationInputTokens":29830,"webSearchRequests":0,"costU