lude name (kebab-case) and description with trigger phrases and negative scope","Minimum 3 codebase-specific file references required","Must contain a verification/testing section","No generic programming phrases allowed","No angle-bracket placeholders in frontmatter"]},{"name":"validate-subagent.sh (custom subagent validator)","config_path":"scripts/validate-subagent.sh","purpose":"Validates generated Claude Code subagent files: frontmatter, name/description fields with trigger phrases, tool scoping, minimum codebase-specific references","enforced_in_ci":false,"has_pre_commit":false,"key_rules":["Frontmatter must have name and description with trigger phrases","Tool scoping must match stated purpose","Minimum 3 codebase-specific file references"]}]},"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"b0762fe0-5d65-43db-a6f1-5be0f02d069e"}
